{"type": "article", "id": 46416, "title": "这个不装菜的便当盒，想帮你收纳苹果配件｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-10-23T23:08:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 44926, "name": "Function 101"}, {"id": 44927, "name": "台虎精酿"}, {"id": 44928, "name": "贝印"}, {"id": 27294, "name": "Federico Babina"}, {"id": 44929, "name": "Scott Jarvie"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 107, "image": "img/article/article_show/201710231705348D9J1eyBSvVFiCH5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 15.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Bento Stack by Function 101</h3><p>来自美国拉斯维加斯的 <a href=\"https://function101.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Function 101</a> 是一个致力于开发苹果配件的设计团队，他们的最新产品是一个旨在满足“果粉”收纳需求的“便当盒”。借鉴日本的收纳方法，设计师为现有的大部分苹果配件量身定制了四个分层，分层的隔板还可以根据需要进行调节。类似 Apple Pencil、Apple Watch 表带这类产品，都配专属的固定夹。其中，用来固定表带的夹子还可以翻转，作为手机架使用。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/bento-stack-for-apple-accessories-iphone#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 38 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170554W1snjI3NTR70QOaM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593190\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170554pR9T2inZyrzaWMc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170554QgAdbklxNoBPVMLi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.196246\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710231705549hFkfnGUKbplOLQH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.849662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nyammy by Kai</h3><p>作为一名猫派，想让厨房也充满猫咪的气息？不妨来看看日本品牌<a href=\"http://www.kai-group.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">贝印</a>推出的猫咪主题餐具 Nyammy 系列。锅子、铲子以及汤勺的手柄被设计成一只坐着的猫咪，像是在期待“铲屎官”的投喂。量匙柄的正中央采用镂空设计，前脚刚好可以用作封袋工具挂在袋子上。值得一提的是，它的内侧还标注了 1/2 刻度线。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.kai-group.com/store/products/list/888\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，整套售价为 7480 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170609qvYn7sTHxNIt6jmZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608374\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170609FHcNUQglJMnoWPbx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170609U8b3dVqajrI9HzL0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170609u1MCGW9RqvOFzkjI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170609KOaFPsodmRIrGg73.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Arch Toy by Federico Babina</h3><p>我们<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/tags/27294.html\">多次介绍</a>过的意大利插画家 <a href=\"http://www.federicobabina.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Federico Babina</a> 又有新作品了——和之前几乎“什么都能被建筑化”的插画不同，这次他选择用陶瓷玩具的形式将知名建筑师和他们的代表作联系在一起。在这套 Arch Toy 中，你可以找到勒·柯布西耶、弗兰克·盖里以及奥斯卡·尼迈耶。这是它们的<a href=\"http://federicobabina.bigcartel.com/products\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 150 欧元，每款限量 70 个，都会附赠配套的明信片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170637UPdb51VIshaWLBX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.524450\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170637HrZyfsz03oAMUhWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170637xecVR3FMPXG6bYtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170637jcMEoAiCKlUWDbxT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170637Bvw6dfkgpVZrCFSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.386308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Void Rug by Scott Jarvie</h3><p>在意想不到的地方发现黑洞是英国产品设计师 <a href=\"https://scottjarvie.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Scott Jarvie</a> 通过视错觉地毯系列 Void Rug 给人们带来的惊喜。和 3D 绘画类似，如果不是站在正确的角度观察，很难发现它们的奥妙之处。地毯分为圆形和长方形两种形状，均采用美利奴羊毛手工制作而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710231706548HP7GE6X4vhqLYZs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170654EGS4gC3zoPqydaQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170654JrVqZkKvA6amUHuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710231706540zyMlwesrOaLokS2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FabricKeyboard by MIT Media Lab</h3><p>在未来，布料除了<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/44797.html\">能放音乐</a>之外，或许还能变成乐器让你穿在身上弹曲子。麻省理工媒体实验室的最新发明 <a href=\"https://www.media.mit.edu/projects/FabricKeyboard/overview/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FabricKeyborad</a> 是一块内置多个传感器的感应布料，能够对触碰、按压做出相应的反馈，并将动作转化为对应的音乐。裁切成键盘大小的它能够解决大型乐器携带不便，无法随处练习或是即兴创作的难题，而且用户之后还能通过软件对音乐进行编辑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170717YeANZcl8KRJutBqT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170717tPECSxWlcU7p3e0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651136\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170717i1FpzsuhE57jAbr2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730159\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>love has no label by Taihu Brewing</h3><p>还记得<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/45892.html\">把爱和彩虹放上罐身</a>的可口可乐吗？2013 年成立的台湾精酿啤酒品牌<a href=\"https://www.taihubrewing.com/tw-zh-index/\" rel=\"nofollow\">台虎精酿</a>最近也加入了通过包装支持性别多元以及婚姻平权的行列之中。以“爱没有标签”为概念，这款“彩虹”啤酒罐走的是极简路线，除了主题文字和品牌名之外，只有一个“图片无法显示”的示意图。据悉，它已于 10 月 20 日开始销售，收益将全部捐赠给台湾同志咨询热线协会。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170742v8zn4cgt9jIDKsfl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171023170742dRw8aHiy7fQ1eNqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}